  <brief_title>Obesity-asthma Endophenotype and Diaphragm Mobility in Adolescence</brief_title>
  <official_title>Obesity-asthma Endophenotype: Assessment of Diaphragm Mobility and Muscle Inflammation Markers in the Adolescence</official_title>
