    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adolescents of both sexes, aged 12-21 years;

          -  For the obesity groups, BMI for gender and age equal to or greater than the 97th
             percentile;

          -  Clinical diagnosis of persistent, moderate and severe asthma by a specialist physician
             and its severity classified according to the GINA (Global Initiative Against Asthma)
             criteria.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Adolescents with a diagnosis of cardiovascular, rheumatic, osteoarticular,
             neuromuscular or any other disease that limits the safe performance of the tests
             proposed by the protocol will be excluded; And those who do not agree to participate
             in the study.
      </textblock>
